kListTypeMoods

public static final GnListType kListTypeMoods
The list of supported tempos for music data, has three levels of granularity. The tempos are categorized in levels in increasing order of granularity. Level 1: The meta level, such as Fast Tempo. Level 2: The sub tempo level, such as Very Fast. Level 3: The micro level, which may be displayed as a numeric tempo range, such as 240-249, or a descriptive phrase.
